0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:43:51.000Z","msg":"我見商場重好多人去食飯。"},{"pid":"23080d65864551b7209c6e25af4de123d07e0f56","tid":1569070,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:46:45.000Z","msg":"7仔ok生意不知幾好，我諗至少升左成倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一有遊行生意就爆升"},{"pid":"43bd0b5617d4bf723ced784a1bb56b2bf81ba12f","tid":1569070,"uid":60686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T23:50:08.000Z","msg":"問返佢點解新加坡冇示威都經濟差"},{"pid":"312c9f7e596c9b184df60e94dad0f81783310595","tid":1569070,"uid":83992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:28:51.000Z","msg":"如果人地話依家經濟差點駁好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1569070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1569070</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n新加坡無示威 好和平 經濟仲差過香港"},{"pid":"d4299eb1fe869fe80a29ccb54f1b61b9118d0b04","tid":1569070,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51211a789735a8025c03f6b94e2705fa857c66a1","tid":1569070,"uid":89482,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZVNxKq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZVNxKq.jpg&h=62924343&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:32:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a439e5015b1da2374ee4289d86b9eb7429bc442f","tid":1569070,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:34:26.000Z","msg":"其實如果有人呢個時候仲淨係擔心緊冇遊客、市道轉淡、經濟轉差，到底係幾咁冷血同豬兜嘅心態？<br />\n<br />\n講緊人命、講緊成個社會體制崩壞、講緊基本人權逐漸喪失，而你眼中只有錢。有冇人同你講，就算你賺幾多，冇制度保障公平、冇制度保證資產，咁你賺嚟把撚咩。<br />\n<br />\n講緊警權過大、講緊人身安全，係黑警睇你唔順眼就可以拉鳩你，福建幫理撚得你咩政見見人就打，你就算買得起成皮嘢一件黑色T-shirt，都可能因為恐懼而冇得著呀，講錢？<br />\n<br />\n怨示威搞到經濟差，點解唔怨林鄭唔揀6月9號撤回就乜事都冇？你地近年食大陸條水賺到風生水起，而家賺少幾個月就嘈？你地賺得多嗰陣有冇回饋過個社會呀？<br />\n<br />\n我都好中意錢呀，但錢唔係大撚晒。而家連李嘉誠都比人批鬥做曱甴啦，尊嚴呀，是非呀，安全呀，錢你老母咩。<br />\n<br />\nー<br />\n攝：蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2436705493112266&amp;id=453118411470994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2436705493112266%26id%3D453118411470994&d=XCDgL7937Usx1GlZVM45wWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=a5ee1822\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2436705493112266&amp;id=453118411470994</a>"},{"pid":"9e25fb94fc5cfda0103183e49e4ee842e616ced4","tid":1569070,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:35:08.000Z","msg":"一早講左推送中外資會走經濟會差架啦，而家應驗囉"},{"pid":"0710e0d34db46a10e62d4ecb5d329379a1226a78","tid":1569070,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791bacc18455dbb1b5193a92121a03b73a0f464a","tid":1569070,"uid":71139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:36:13.000Z","msg":"講經濟差，講整都係旅遊業，仲要係內地團嗰啲，佢地一條龍式搭車買野食飯酒店都同一個老闆，真係關香港人撚事。"},{"pid":"7af3856cc634ca43c5e0def6dbe99c50fdced79e","tid":1569070,"uid":249243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2d252b3e58a13e89175bda8181cf24f29173284","tid":1569070,"uid":135959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:36:22.000Z","msg":"黨鐵大增人手，夜晚加班痴磚拆欄，大增就業機會！"},{"pid":"93c78cb7bc208e4ab81bf75f3a9bbe175a1e640d","tid":1569070,"uid":300424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:37:07.000Z","msg":"重建經濟新秩序<br />\n地產霸權 令企業 經營困難<br />\n民不聊生"},{"pid":"d2a101e9f78085e0232420b5d23003476f509050","tid":1569070,"uid":195176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:37:43.000Z","msg":"亂世中搵唔到食係個人能力問題, 同其他人無關"},{"pid":"5df4e347ab6bd4c2cad3ad9349d67ace6fa1d677","tid":1569070,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:38:1